cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.CR 

This paper discusses scientometric indicators for assessing the impact of scholars, which is a topic related to digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), cybernetics (cs.CY), social and information networks (cs.SI), and cryptography and security (cs.CR). However, since the paper focuses on the construction and application of these indicators rather than their theoretical foundations, cs.DL and cs.IR are the most likely sub-categories.
